  "body": "### Description\r\nThis component is used in the MessageView delegate. This delegate needs to be as simple as possible and we need to avoid any backend calls when creating/binding the delegate.\r\n\r\nLinksMessageView is doing a lot of data parsing and it's also calling the backend for extra information. The purpose of this task is to analyse the component and refactor it in order to achieve:\r\n\r\n- [ ] Improved creation time\r\n- [ ] Improved component design",
