    "body": "@micieslak there is also this issue #9084 and @mprakhov suggested the status-go validation approach taking this into consideration. \r\nFrom my understanding (@mprakhov please correct me if I got it wrong) on status-go there will be two changes:\r\n1. Download the preview data for all whitelisted links (now we download the preview data only for some links. For other links we send the url in the UI)\r\n2. Validate the preview before sending it to the UI\r\n\r\nIn the UI we will use the raw data/filename provided by status-go. And we could easily mock this.\r\n\r\nIMO this change is good and it will help us better design the component.",
